'''Tasedmirt n twaksa''' d talmest n [[tasedmirt tagmant|tsedmirin tigmanin]] dgi tettili twaksa n snat n tcubarin deg [[acubar|ucubar]] aẓaṛan deg yiwen n userrif neɣ sin n iserrifen, s wakka ad yelfu [[aseṛw|uraseṛwu]] n ucubar 

Tamahilt-a tettusemma Tawaksa tafnazayt, Tella telmest s wazal-is n tsedmirin n twaksa tla [[alkan|talkanin]] s talɣa tamatant yakk d [[tagrawt n tanaft]] yessedmiren d [[izeffaren d ilugan n Lewis|ilugan n Lewis]] i wakken ad tgi (ad ttexdem) [[alkin]]

Tettwassen (tettusemma) tzukt n userrif amyiwen d umsin s tsedmirin E1 reaction d E2 reaction, s [[asnay|wesnay]]

== Tazukt E1 ==

* Aserrif amezwar:
<div style="direction:ltr;text-align:center;"> (CH<sub>3</sub>)<sub>3</sub>C-Br
→ (CH<sub>3</sub>)<sub>3</sub>C<sup>+</sup> + Br<sup>-</sup>
</div>
* Aserrif wis sin :
<div style="direction:ltr;text-align:center;"> (CH<sub>3</sub>)<sub>3</sub>C<sup>+</sup>
→ (CH<sub>3</sub>)<sub>2</sub>C=CH<sub>2</sub> + H<sup>+</sup>
</div>

== Tazukt E2 ==

<div style="direction:ltr;text-align:center;"> (CH<sub>3</sub> - CH<sub>2</sub> - Br) + OH<sup>-</sup> →
CH<sub>2</sub>=CH<sub>2</sub> + H<sub>2</sub>O + Br<sup>-</sup>
</div>
